OL,3,CMakerfield by-election: Declared
OL,4,Ccandidates and everything else you
OL,5,Cneed to know
OL,7,FA by-election in the parliamentary
OL,8,Fseat of Makerfield is being held after
OL,9,Fthe resignation of Josh Simons.
OL,11,FLabour currently holds a majority of
OL,12,F5,399 in Makerfield, with Reform in
OL,13,Fsecond, with 18% of the vote.
OL,15,FBut in Wigan, which includes part of
OL,16,FMakerfield, Labour lost all 22 of its
OL,17,Fcouncillors in the local election,
OL,18,Fwith Reform picking up 24 of the 25
OL,19,Fseats up for grabs.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
