OL,3,CMakerfield by-election: Declared
OL,4,Ccandidates and everything else you
OL,5,Cneed to know
OL,7,FIn the eight Makerfield wards that
OL,8,Fvoted in the local election, Reform
OL,9,Fsecured 50% of the vote while Labour
OL,10,Fgot 23%.
OL,12,FThe constituency's former MP stood
OL,13,Fdown to allow the Mayor of Greater
OL,14,FManchester Andy Burnham to stand for
OL,15,Fhis seat and return to Westminster.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
