OL,3,CMakerfield by-election: Declared
OL,4,Ccandidates and everything else you
OL,5,Cneed to know
OL,7,FThe full list of candidates, in
OL,8,Falphabetical order, standing in the by-
OL,9,Felection, which is expected to be held
OL,10,Fat the end of June are:
OL,12,FAndy Burnham (Labour)
OL,14,FThe current Mayor of Greater
OL,15,FManchester has been announced as
OL,16,FLabour's candidate for the Makerfield
OL,17,Fby-election.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
