PN,39705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1779808265
OL,3,CMakerfield by-election: Declared
OL,4,Ccandidates and everything else you
OL,5,Cneed to know
OL,7,FThe three-time Mayor and former MP for
OL,8,FLeigh told ITV News: "I'm standing on
OL,9,Fa call for change, aren't I? I think
OL,10,Fwe need to change Labour to some
OL,11,Fdegree so we can change politics,
OL,12,Fchange the country."
OL,14,FHe said: "For me, we need a different
OL,15,Fpath that puts those things back under
OL,16,Fpublic control, makes them more
OL,17,Faffordable.
OL,19,F"The path that Britain has been on for
OL,20,F40 years, in my view, has been the
OL,21,Fwrong path.
OL,26,@pD@VOUtD@TO]vD@JOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1779808265
OL,3,CMakerfield by-election: Declared
OL,4,Ccandidates and everything else you
OL,5,Cneed to know
OL,7,F"It's taken us to this place where
OL,8,Fpeople can't afford life's basics,
OL,9,Fthey can't afford a few pints at the
OL,10,Fweekend, they can't afford a holiday.
OL,11,FAnd that's why they're saying to
OL,12,Fpoliticians, do better. This is not
OL,13,Fgood enough. And they're right to say
OL,14,Fthat.
OL,16,F"I'm saying there's a new path here,
OL,17,Fnew politics to build a new economy
OL,18,Ffor Britain."
OL,26,@zD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
