SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1779808265
OL,3,CMakerfield by-election: Declared
OL,4,Ccandidates and everything else you
OL,5,Cneed to know
OL,7,F"That is the main question in this by-
OL,8,Felection. Are people happy to stick on
OL,9,Fthe path that Britain's been on for 40
OL,10,Fyears, or do we want a new path?"
OL,12,FAlan 'Howlin' Laud Hope (Monster
OL,13,FRaving Loony Party)
OL,15,FParty leader and co-founder Alan
OL,16,F'Howlin' Laud Hope is the candidate
OL,17,Ffor the Monster Raving Loony party in
OL,18,Fthe Makerfield by-election.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
