SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1779808265
OL,3,CMakerfield by-election: Declared
OL,4,Ccandidates and everything else you
OL,5,Cneed to know
OL,7,FHe previously stood in the Runcorn and
OL,8,FHelsby by-election, where he received
OL,9,F128 votes.
OL,11,FRobert Kenyon (Reform UK)
OL,13,FMakerfield-born plumber and gas
OL,14,Fengineer Robert Kenyon is Reform UK's
OL,15,Fcandidate for the Makerfield by-
OL,16,Felection.
OL,18,FIn a campaign video, he claimed to be
OL,19,Fthe first MP born in Makerfield to
OL,20,Frepresent the constituency.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1779808265
OL,3,CMakerfield by-election: Declared
OL,4,Ccandidates and everything else you
OL,5,Cneed to know
OL,7,FHe said: "It get's me a bit emotional
OL,8,Fsometimes, thinking that I could be
OL,9,Frepresenting people in Parliament.
OL,10,FIt's a massive honour. People are
OL,11,Fgoing to think: hang on, he serviced
OL,12,Fmy boiler last week.
OL,14,F"People in this area have been taken
OL,15,Fadvantage of for too long. The
OL,16,FMakerfield constituency deserves a
OL,17,Flocal champion."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
