OL,3,CMakerfield by-election: Declared
OL,4,Ccandidates and everything else you
OL,5,Cneed to know
OL,7,FKenyon stood in the constituency for
OL,8,FReform UK in the 2024 general
OL,9,Felection, where he came second to
OL,10,FLabour's Josh Simons.
OL,12,FRebecca Shepherd (Restore Britain)
OL,14,FLocal businesswoman Rebecca Shepherd
OL,15,Fhas been announced as Restore
OL,16,FBritain's candidate for the Makerfield
OL,17,Fby-election.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
