OL,3,CMakerfield by-election: Declared
OL,4,Ccandidates and everything else you
OL,5,Cneed to know
OL,7,FA party statement said: "Rebecca has
OL,8,Fspent most of her adult life living
OL,9,Fand working in the Wigan borough,
OL,10,Fwhere she has built and run her own
OL,11,Fsmall business.
OL,13,F"Through that experience, she
OL,14,Funderstands first-hand the pressures
OL,15,Ffacing local businesses and working
OL,16,Fpeople across the community."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/13
